{"tid":2515750,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"被巴菲特批評助長賭博 Robinhood反擊 ： 人們已厭倦巴菲特是唯一的投資聖言","createTime":"2021-05-04T07:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T09:33:37.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"11b153c8f402c338b3bbf19714db45134f92a1f5","tid":2515750,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:51:16.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕「股神」巴菲特（Warren Buffett）旗下波克夏海瑟威（Berkshire Hathaway）年度股東大會上週六登場，會中巴菲特、副董事長孟格（Charlie Munger）皆發言批評去年開始的散戶投資熱潮，並點名無佣金線上交易平台羅賓漢（Robinhood）是罪魁禍首。羅賓漢週一則發文回擊，稱大家已厭倦巴菲特和孟格是唯一的「投資聖言」。<br />\n<br />\n《雅虎財經》報導，巴菲特當時表示羅賓漢助長許多新手投資人進入股票市場，基本上是在賭博。他聲稱，羅賓漢沒有違法、沒有不道德之處，但在富裕社會中利用人們賭博天性來賺錢的人不值得欽佩<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n羅賓漢公關負責人萊姆希（Jacqueline Oritz Ramsay）週一在一篇文章反擊，稱公司不會坐視巴菲特或孟格這類人繼續控制普通人的投資生涯，正是因為羅賓漢打開了金融市場的大門，才讓這些往日大咖對變遷感到不安，並說羅賓漢的大多數用戶都在買進、持有（而非賣空或賭博）。<br />\n<br />\n羅賓漢補充，如今美國的散戶投資蓬勃發展，而科技是散戶們公平競爭的最大利器，羅賓漢正是要提供平等的機會和普及性，像是零股交易便讓資金較少的人可以入場。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3520413\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3520413&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=31cd9872\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3520413&h=0256e018\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3520413</a>"},{"pid":"4c6c28a563c1cb6de09883a1e7f2cb848e8a2260","tid":2515750,"uid":36845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:52:33.000Z","msg":"又講得幾好"},{"pid":"a391c3f2fe9a181722efce94806c69bdff168919","tid":2515750,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:53:51.000Z","msg":"Robinhood 連登仔上身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4823daa9408143899828690adc644a52d8c99a","tid":2515750,"uid":243380,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"條廢老最多都係9up兩句<br />\nRobinhood直頭干擾自由市場運作<br />\n收皮啦"},{"pid":"ed9f2949ba02a8159bed54e6fb8601a822d16a78","tid":2515750,"uid":180576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:55:36.000Z","msg":"GME單野呢"},{"pid":"9a050b90a980b8c9682d107ad368079acab97b03","tid":2515750,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:56:00.000Z","msg":"是但啦，投資最緊要開心"},{"pid":"de7edcead1bf2af1f7e87bffd82da3b6c5cc458f","tid":2515750,"uid":54552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:57:43.000Z","msg":"之前GME 事件已經睇穿robinhood 啦 扮晒嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做生意一燒埋自己度就唔俾交易 只贏不輸 點够你玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2277b926039b1d839f8157a741f4c80ad250aca1","tid":2515750,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:59:40.000Z","msg":"塊面皮好𠹌厚"},{"pid":"78d6c5d9ce1557d25ecf60e4360964d75b7a44c9","tid":2515750,"uid":140893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:01:04.000Z","msg":"菲比斯話robinhood助長散戶賭博無錯啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2264e30f8aeede3394ec74b3cccb3b426af9df","tid":2515750,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:01:08.000Z","msg":"年輕人已經放棄左廢老"},{"pid":"5275667dcd3fd206c6ab0033bc0b01e70a22c77a","tid":2515750,"uid":107231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"兩邊都係仆街<br />\n我只信Elon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47aca05833cad668ed9ee82c60c61ac6d2303132","tid":2515750,"uid":140893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5275667dcd3fd206c6ab0033bc0b01e70a22c77a","tid":2515750,"uid":107231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-0